snippet.title: Speed or Death Trailer (PS4/PS5, Switch Asia)
snippet.description:
Drive for your life!

Cross a city infested with enormous monsters, dodge the fiery breath of a dragon, find how to escape an alien invasion... all without getting eaten by a worm. 

This is Speed or Death, a frenzied racing game where the most important thing isn’t reaching the finish line, but surviving the chaos around you. Unlock different cars and live to tell the tale another day. What apocalypse shall we race through today?

Game details:
